preqs: ECE3091 or completion of 132 credit points

rules.ruleString: (Must have passed a unit in {ECE3091} OR  Must have passed 132 credit points)

description: Together with ECE4095 Project B, this unit is a challenging opportunity to pursue independently an individual project and is likely to require extended effort. The two units together normally include a preparatory literature survey and developmental work such as design, construction and programming. Students choose a project that interests them, and are assigned to a team of two supervising staff members.
